text:【战“疫”手册：ECMO究竟是什么？还有哪些设备用于治疗新冠肺炎？】ECMO is a word that we have frequently heard in the treatment for the novel coronavirus disease (COVID-19). It refers to a machine which can temporarily replace the functions of the heart and lungs. It operates by pumping venous blood from the body, artificially oxygenating it and then pumping it back into the arteries. Besides ECMO, other technologies have been applied in the treatment of COVID-19. For more: http://t.cn/A678EsKv
